{
  "title": "Charred Crispy Turkish Monkfish Adana Kebap",
  "description": "A Jain-friendly Turkish dish featuring monkfish, served as a solo dinner, with a charred and crispy texture, rendered in fat, and formed as Adana kebap",
  "cuisine": "Turkish",
